#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; is a program for viewing, extracting, creating and modifying archives. "
"&ark; can handle various archive formats such as <command>tar</command>, "
"<command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, <command>zip</command>, "
"<command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, <command>xz</command>, "
"<command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command>, <command>deb</command>, "
"<command>xar</command> and <command>AppImage</command> (support for certain "
"archive formats depends on the appropriate command-line programs being "
"installed)."
msgstr ""
"&ark; je program za pregledovanje, ekstrahiranje, ustvarjanje in "
"spreminjanje arhivov. &ark; lahko obdeluje različne formate arhivov, kot so "
"<command>tar</command>, <command>gzip</command>, <command>bzip2</command>, "
"<command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>7zip</command>, "
"<command>xz</command>, <command>rpm</command>, <command>cab</command>, "
"<command>deb</command>, <command>xar</command> and <command>AppImage</"
"command> (podpora za nekatere oblike arhivov je odvisna od namestitve "
"ustreznih programov ukazne vrstice)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ark;'s main window"
msgstr "&ark;ovo glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to successfully use &ark;, you need KDE Frameworks 5. The library "
"libarchive version 3.1 or above is needed to handle most archive types, "
"including tar, compressed tar, rpm, deb and cab archives. To handle other "
"file formats, you need the appropriate command line programs, such as "
"<command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</command>, <command>7z</"
"command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</command> and "
"<command>lrzip</command>."
msgstr ""
"Za uspešno uporabo &ark; potrebujete KDE Frameworks 5. Knjižnica libarchive "
"različice 3.1 ali višje je potrebna za obdelavo večine vrst arhivov, "
"vključno z arhivi tar, stisnjenimi tar, rpm, deb in cab arhivi. Za obdelavo "
"drugih formatov datotek potrebujete ustrezne programe ukazne vrstice, kot so "
"<command>zipinfo</command>, <command>zip</command>, <command>unzip</"
"command>, <command>rar</command>, <command>unrar</command>, <command>7z</"
"command>, <command>lsar</command>, <command>unar</command> in "
"<command>lrzip</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &ark;"
msgstr "Uporaba &ark;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening Archives"
msgstr "Odpiranje arhivov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open an archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. You can also open archive files by dragging "
"and dropping from &dolphin;. Archive files should be associated with &ark;, "
"so you can also <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click a file in &dolphin; "
"and select <guimenuitem>Open with &ark;</guimenuitem> to open it or select "
"an extract action for this file."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti arhiv v &ark;, izberite <guimenuitem>Odpri...</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo>) v meniju <guimenu>Arhiv</guimenu>. Arhivske datoteke lahko "
"odprete tudi tako, da jih povlečete in spustite iz &dolphin;. Arhivske "
"datoteke bi morale biti povezane z &ark;, zato lahko tudi "
"<mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> kliknete datoteko v &dolphin; in izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Odpri z &ark;</guimenuitem>, da jo odprete ali izberete dejanje "
"ekstrahiraj za izpis te datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have enabled the information panel in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"menu additional information about the selected folders or files in the "
"archive is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v meniju <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> omogočili informacijsko "
"ploščo, so prikazane dodatne informacije o izbranih mapah ali datotekah v "
"arhivu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Operations"
msgstr "Arhivske operacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Various operations can be performed for an opened archive by using the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. For example, you can save the archive with "
"a different name using <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>. Archive "
"properties such as type, size and MD5 hash can be viewed using the "
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> item."
msgstr ""
"Za odprti arhiv lahko z uporabo menija <guimenu>Arhiv</guimenu> izvedete "
"različne operacije. Arhiv lahko na primer shranite z drugim imenom z uporabo "
"<guimenuitem>Shrani kot...</guimenuitem>. Lastnosti arhiva, kot so vrsta, "
"velikost in vrednost MD5 razprševanja, si lahko ogledate s pomočjo elementa "
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has the ability to test archives for integrity. This functionality is "
"currently available for <command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command> and "
"<command>7z</command> archives. The test action can be found in the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"&ark; ima možnost testiranja celovitosti arhivov. Ta funkcionalnost je "
"trenutno na voljo za arhive <command>zip</command>, <command>rar</command> "
"in <command>7z</command>. Testno dejanje je na voljo v meniju "
"<guimenu>Arhiv</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive Comments"
msgstr "Komentarji arhiva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; can handle comments embedded in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</"
"literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archives."
msgstr ""
"&ark; lahko obdeluje komentarje, vgrajene v <literal role=\"extension\">zip</"
"literal> in <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Comments embedded in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> archives are "
"automatically displayed."
msgstr ""
"Komentarji, vstavljeni v <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> arhive, "
"se samodejno prikažejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archives you can modify a "
"comment with the actions <guimenuitem>Add Comment</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Edit comment</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> arhivov lahko spremenite "
"komentar z dejanji <guimenuitem>Dodaj komentar</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Urejanje komentarja</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) iz menija <guimenu>Arhiv</guimenu>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a comment"
msgstr "Urejanje komentarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The comment menu item is enabled only for <literal role=\"extension\">rar</"
"literal> archives."
msgstr ""
"Element menija Komentar je omogočen samo za <literal role=\"extension\">rar</"
"literal> arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a comment from a <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> archive "
"delete the text in the comment window."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti komentar iz <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal> "
"arhiva, izbrišite besedilo v oknu s komentarji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Files"
msgstr "Delo z datotekami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once an archive has been opened, you can perform various operations on the "
"files inside the archive. By selecting a file and using the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu, you can choose different operations to perform:"
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete arhiv, lahko z datotekami v njem izvajate različne operacije. Z "
"izbiro datoteke in uporabo menija <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> lahko izberete "
"različne operacije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>) will open the file with &ark;'s internal "
"viewer. This is a fast read-only viewer, but does not support all file types."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>) bo odprl datoteko z notranjim "
"pregledovalnikom &ark;. To je hiter pregledovalnik samo za branje, vendar ne "
"podpira vseh vrst datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> will open the file in the associated "
"application for that file type."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Odpri</guimenuitem> bo odprl datoteko v povezani aplikaciji za "
"to vrsto datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Open With...</guimenuitem> allows you to choose which "
"application to open the file with."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Odpri z...</guimenuitem> vam omogoča, da izberete aplikacijo, s "
"katero želite odpreti datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) This action allows to change names of both "
"files and folders. As in the Dolphin file manager, this action can be called "
"via a shortcut and renaming is done via inline editing. There are also "
"filename checks provided, which prevent usage of invalid characters such as "
"<userinput>/</userinput>, <userinput>.</userinput> and <userinput>..</"
"userinput> in filenames."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Preimenuj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) To dejanje omogoča spreminjanje imen datotek "
"in map. Tako kot v upravljalniku datotek Dolphin lahko to dejanje prikličete "
"z bližnjico, preimenovanje pa se izvede z urejanjem v vrstici. Zagotovljeni "
"so tudi pregledi imen datotek, ki preprečujejo uporabo neveljavnih znakov, "
"kot so <userinput>/</userinput>, <userinput>.</userinput> in <userinput>..</"
"userinput> v imenih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> (<keycap>Del</keycap>) will remove the "
"currently selected file(s) from the archive. Note that this action is "
"undoable."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem> (<keycap>Del</keycap>) odstrani trenutno "
"izbrano(-e) datoteko(-e) iz arhiva. Upoštevajte, da je to dejanje mogoče "
"dokončno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) opens a submenu with previously accessed "
"folders, and you can choose to quickly extract into any of these or browse "
"to a non-listed folder. See the next section for more details on extraction."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ekstrahiraj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>) odpre podmeni s predhodno dostopnimi mapami, "
"pri čemer se lahko odločite za hiter izvleček v katero koli od njih ali "
"brskanje po mapi, ki ni na seznamu. Za več podrobnosti o ekstrakciji glejte "
"naslednje poglavje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</"
"keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo>): As in typical file managers, moving, pasting and copying are "
"provided. Users can move or copy files from different folders (which are "
"expandable in the tree view) and paste them to the same destination at once. "
"A folder can be copied into itself, but can not be moved. There are also "
"checks for conflicting filenames: You won't be able to copy or move files "
"into a folder that has entries with the same names - that could lead to data "
"loss."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo>) / <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>) / "
"<guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>): Kot v tipičnih upravljalnikih datotek so na "
"voljo premikanje, prilepljanje in kopiranje. Uporabniki lahko premaknejo ali "
"kopirajo datoteke iz različnih map (ki jih je mogoče razširiti v drevesnem "
"prikazu) in jih hkrati prilepijo na isti cilj. Mapo lahko kopirate med "
"seboj, ne morete pa je premakniti. Preverja tudi nasprotujoča si imena "
"datotek: datotek ne boste mogli kopirati ali premakniti v mapo, ki ima vnose "
"z enakimi imeni, kar bi lahko povzročilo izgubo podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Add Files</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) This action can be used to add files at any "
"location within the archive. If you select a folder and use this action, "
"files will be added to the selected folder. Otherwise, the new files will be "
"added to the root of the archive."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Dodaj datoteke</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) To dejanje lahko uporabite za dodajanje "
"datotek na katero koli mesto v arhivu. Če izberete mapo in uporabite to "
"dejanje, bodo datoteke dodane v izbrano mapo. V nasprotnem primeru bodo nove "
"datoteke dodane v koren arhiva."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Files"
msgstr "Urejanje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you edit and save a file which you opened using <guimenuitem>Open</"
"guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Open With...</guimenuitem>, Ark will ask you if "
"you want to update the file in the archive. If you answer Yes, the archive "
"will be updated with the saved file."
msgstr ""
"Če uredite in shranite datoteko, ki ste jo odprli z uporabo "
"<guimenuitem>Odpri</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Odpri z...</guimenuitem>, "
"vas bo Ark vprašal, ali želite posodobiti datoteko v arhivu. Če odgovorite "
"Da, bo arhiv posodobljen s shranjeno datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extracting Files"
msgstr "Ekstrahiranje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once an archive has been opened in &ark;, it can be extracted. This can be "
"done by selecting <guisubmenu>Extract</guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu. This opens a submenu with previously accessed folders, and "
"you can choose to quickly extract into any of these. Alternatively, select "
"the submenu item <guisubmenu>Extract To...</guisubmenu> to open the "
"<guilabel>Extract</guilabel> dialog, where you can set various options that "
"affect the extraction. See below for information on the available options in "
"the Extract dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko arhiv odprete v programu &ark;, ga lahko ekstrahirate. To lahko storite "
"tako, da v meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> izberete "
"<guisubmenu>Ekstrahiraj</guisubmenu>. Odpre se podmeni s prej dostopnimi "
"mapami, v katere lahko hitro shranite izvleček. Lahko pa izberete element "
"podmenija <guisubmenu>Ekstrahiraj v...</guisubmenu>, da odprete pogovorno "
"okno <guilabel>Ekstrahiraj</guilabel>, v katerem lahko nastavite različne "
"možnosti, ki vplivajo na ekstrakcijo. Informacije o razpoložljivih možnostih "
"v pogovornem oknu Ekstrahiranje si oglejte spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guibutton>Extract</guibutton> button in the toolbar to "
"access the same extraction options."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do istih možnosti ekstrakcije lahko uporabite tudi gumb "
"<guibutton>Ekstrahiraj</guibutton> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extract the entire archive, you can select <guisubmenu>Extract All</"
"guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu. This action "
"unconditionally extracts all files in the archive."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvleči celoten arhiv, lahko v meniju <guimenu>Arhiv</guimenu> "
"izberete <guisubmenu>Ekstrahiraj vse</guisubmenu>. To dejanje brezpogojno "
"ekstrahira vse datoteke v arhivu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to extract files and folders by simply dragging them with the "
"mouse to a folder in &dolphin;."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke in mape je mogoče izvleči tako, da jih preprosto povlečete z miško "
"v mapo v &dolphin;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: Extracting files from an archive does not change the archive and its "
"contents."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: Izvlečenje datotek iz arhiva ne spremeni arhiva in njegove vsebine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Extract dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno ekstrahiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Extract</guilabel> dialog allows you to choose where the files "
"will be extracted to. The default location is the folder the archive is in. "
"The dialog can also be opened by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"V pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Ekstrahiraj</guilabel> lahko izberete, kam se "
"bodo datoteke izvlekle. Privzeta lokacija je mapa, v kateri je arhiv. "
"Pogovorno okno lahko odprete tudi tako, da pritisnete <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ark;'s Extract dialog"
msgstr "&ark;ovo Ekstrahiraj pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can specify to extract the files into a subfolder. The default name of "
"this subfolder is the archive name without the filename extension, but you "
"can edit it to your needs. If you want to preserve paths when extracting, "
"select the <guilabel>Preserve paths when extracting</guilabel> option. You "
"may also choose to open the destination folder in &dolphin; or close &ark; "
"once the extraction is complete."
msgstr ""
"Določite lahko, da se datoteke ekstrahirajo v podmapo. Privzeto ime te "
"podmape je ime arhiva brez končnice, vendar ga lahko uredite po svojih "
"potrebah. Če želite ohraniti poti pri ekstrahiranju, izberite možnost "
"<guilabel>Ohrani poti med ekstrahiranjem</guilabel>. Po končanem "
"ekstrahiranju lahko ciljno mapo odprete tudi v programu &dolphin; ali "
"zaprete program &ark;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If one or more files in the archive list are highlighted, you can also "
"select which files to extract:"
msgstr ""
"Če je ena ali več datotek na seznamu arhivov označena, lahko izberete tudi "
"datoteke, ki jih želite ekstrahirati:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Selected files only</guilabel> extracts only the files which have "
"been selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Samo izbrane datoteke</guilabel> ekstrahira samo izbrane datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>All files</guilabel> extracts the entire contents of the archive."
msgstr "<guilabel>Vse datoteke</guilabel> ekstrahira celotno vsebino arhiva."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Archives and Adding Files"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje arhivov in dodajanje datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new archive in &ark;, choose <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) from the "
"<guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti nov arhiv v &ark;, izberite <guimenuitem>Novo</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo>) v meniju <guimenu>Arhiv</guimenu>."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create an archive"
msgstr "Ustvari arhiv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then type the name of the archive, with the appropriate extension "
"(<literal role=\"extension\">tar.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">zip</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal>, &etc;) or select "
"a supported format in the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> combo box and check "
"the <guilabel>Automatically add <replaceable>filename extension</"
"replaceable></guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Nato lahko vnesete ime arhiva z ustrezno končnico (<literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal "
"role=\"extension\">7z</literal>, &etc;) ali pa v izbirnem polju "
"<guilabel>Filter</guilabel> izberete podprto obliko in potrdite možnost "
"<guilabel>Avtomatsko dodaj <replaceable>pripono imena datoteke</"
"replaceable></guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add files or folders to the new archive, choose <guimenuitem>Add Files..."
"</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Archive</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v nov arhiv dodati datoteke ali mape, izberite <guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"datoteke...</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenuitem>Arhiv</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alternative way to add files to an archive is to drag one or more files "
"from e.g. &dolphin; into the main &ark; window, and it will be added to the "
"current archive. Note that files added in this way will always be added to "
"the root directory of the archive."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost dodajanja datotek v arhiv je, da povlečete eno ali več datotek "
"iz npr. &dolphin; v glavno okno &ark; in te bodo dodane v trenutni arhiv. "
"Upoštevajte, da bodo tako dodane datoteke vedno dodane v korenski imenik "
"arhiva."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional options are presented in collapsible groups at the bottom of the "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne možnosti so predstavljene v zložljivih skupinah na dnu pogovornega "
"okna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compression"
msgstr "Stiskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A higher value generates smaller archives, but results in longer compression "
"and decompression times. The default compression level proposed by &ark; is "
"usually a good compromise between size and (de)compression speed. For most "
"formats the minimum compression level is equivalent to just storing the "
"files, &ie; applying no compression."
msgstr ""
"Večja vrednost ustvari manjše arhive, vendar povzroči daljše čase stiskanja "
"in raztezanje. Privzeta stopnja stiskanja, ki jo predlaga &ark;, je običajno "
"dober kompromis med velikostjo in hitrostjo (de)stiskanja. Pri večini "
"formatov je najmanjša stopnja stiskanja enaka samo shranjevanju datotek, "
"torej brez stiskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">7z</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> archives you "
"can select between different compression methods."
msgstr ""
"Za arhive <literal role=\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">7z</literal> in <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> "
"lahko izberete različne metode stiskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that using compression methods other than the pre-selected defaults may "
"limit compatibility with file archivers. For example, opening <literal role="
"\"extension\">zip</literal> archives with compression methods other than "
"<quote>Deflate</quote> requires newer archiving software."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko uporaba metod stiskanja, ki niso predizbrane kot "
"privzete, omeji združljivost z datotečnimi arhivatorji. Za odpiranje "
"<literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> arhivov z drugimi metodami "
"stiskanja kot <quote>Izprazni</quote> je na primer potrebna novejša "
"programska oprema za arhiviranje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password Protection"
msgstr "Zaščita z geslom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create a <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal> and "
"<literal role=\"extension\">jar</literal> archive you can protect it with a "
"password. Currently, only the <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> "
"format supports multiple encryption methods. For other formats that support "
"only one encryption method, the method is shown in the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Če ustvarite arhiv <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal> in "
"<literal role=\"extension\">jar</literal>, ga lahko zaščitite z geslom. "
"Trenutno samo format <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal> podpira več "
"načinov šifriranja. Pri drugih formatih, ki podpirajo samo eno metodo "
"šifriranja, je metoda prikazana v spustnem polju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other encryption methods than the default <guilabel>ZipCrypto</guilabel> "
"might not be supported by all file archivers."
msgstr ""
"Drugi načini šifriranja kot privzeti <guilabel>ZipCrypto</guilabel> morda "
"niso podprti v vseh datotečnih arhivih."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a password protected archive"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje arhiva, zaščitenega z geslom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose whether to require the password before showing the list of files. "
"This is called header encryption and is available only with the <literal "
"role=\"extension\">rar</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</"
"literal> formats. Header encryption is enabled by default (when available), "
"in order to offer the maximum protection for novice users."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, ali naj se pred prikazom seznama datotek zahteva geslo. To se "
"imenuje šifriranje glave in je na voljo samo v formatih <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal> in <literal role=\"extension\">7zip</literal>. "
"Šifriranje glave je privzeto omogočeno (če je na voljo), da bi zagotovili "
"največjo zaščito za uporabnike začetnike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multi-volume Archive"
msgstr "Arhiv v več nosilcih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">rar</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal> formats you "
"can create multi-volume archives, also known as multi-part or split archives."
msgstr ""
"S formati <literal role=\"extension\">zip</literal>, <literal role="
"\"extension\">rar</literal> in <literal role=\"extension\">7z</literal> "
"lahko ustvarite več-zvezne arhive, znane tudi kot večdelne ali deljene "
"arhive."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A multi-volume archive is one big compressed archive split into several "
"files. This feature is useful if the maximum file size is limited, &eg; by "
"the capacity of a storage medium or the maximal size of an email with "
"attachments."
msgstr ""
"Večdelni arhiv je en velik stisnjen arhiv, razdeljen na več datotek. Ta "
"funkcija je uporabna, če je največja velikost datoteke omejena, &eg; glede "
"na kapaciteto pomnilniškega medija ali največjo velikost elektronskega "
"sporočila s priponkami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a multi-volume archive, check the <guilabel>Create multi-volume "
"archive</guilabel> checkbox and set a maximum <guilabel>Volume size</"
"guilabel> in the dialog. Then add all files to the archive and &ark; will "
"automatically generate the required number of archive volumes. Depending on "
"the selected format the files have an extension with consecutively numbering "
"scheme &eg; <filename>xxx.7z.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.7z.002</filename> "
"or <filename>xxx.zip.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.zip.002</filename> or "
"<filename>xxx.part1.rar</filename>, <filename>xxx.part2.rar</filename> &etc;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti arhiv z več nosilci, potrdite polje <guilabel>Ustvari "
"arhiv z več nosilci</guilabel> in v pogovornem oknu nastavite največjo "
"<guilabel>Velikost nosilca</guilabel>. Nato dodajte vse datoteke v arhiv in "
"&ark; bo samodejno ustvaril zahtevano število nosilcev arhiva. Odvisno od "
"izbranega formata imajo datoteke končnico z zaporednim številčenjem &eg; "
"<filename>xxx.7z.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.7z.002</filename> ali "
"<filename>xxx.zip.001</filename>, <filename>xxx.zip.002</filename > ali "
"<filename>xxx.part1.rar</filename>, <filename>xxx.part2.rar</filename> itd."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To extract a multi-volume archive, put all archive files into one folder and "
"open the file with the lowest extension number in &ark; and all other parts "
"of the split archive will be opened automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ekstrahirati arhiv z več nosilci, postavite vse arhivske datoteke "
"v eno mapo in odprite datoteko z najnižjo končnico v &ark; in vsi ostali "
"deli razdeljenega arhiva se bodo odprli samodejno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &ark; in the File Manager"
msgstr "Uporaba &ark; v upravljalniku datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on an archive in a file manager like &dolphin; "
"displays a context menu with an item <guimenuitem>Extract</guimenuitem>. The "
"menu has these additional items to extract an archive using &ark;:"
msgstr ""
"S klikom z &RMB; v arhivu v upravljalniku datotek, kot je &dolphin; se "
"prikaže kontekstni meni z elementom <guimenuitem>Odpri z Ark</guimenuitem>. "
"Meni ima te dodatne elemente za izvlečenje arhiva z &ark;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract here</guimenuitem> creates a subfolder in the folder "
"with the archive and extracts the folders and files into it. In case the "
"archive contains only one file or folder, no subfolder will be created."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Ekstrahiraj sem</guimenuitem> ustvari podmapo v mapi z arhivom "
"in vanjo ekstrahira mape in datoteke. Če arhiv vsebuje samo eno datoteko ali "
"mapo, podmapa ne bo ustvarjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract here and delete archive</guimenuitem> creates a "
"subfolder in the folder with the archive, extracts the folders and files "
"into it and deletes the archive."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izvleci sem in izbriši arhiv</guimenuitem> ustvari podmapo v "
"mapi z arhivom, izvleče mape in datoteke vanjo ter izbriše arhiv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Extract to…</guimenuitem> opens the Extract dialog where you "
"can choose the destination folder and various extraction options."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Izvleci v...</guimenuitem> odpre pogovorno okno Izvleci, kjer "
"lahko izberete ciljno mapo in različne možnosti izvlačevanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dolphin;'s context menu for a selection of files and/or folders displays "
"these actions in the <guimenu>Compress</guimenu> submenu:"
msgstr ""
"&dolphin;ov kontekstni meni za izbiro datotek in/ali map prikaže ta dejanja "
"v podmeniju <guimenu>Stisni</guimenu>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Compress to \"Archive.tar.gz\"</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Compress to \"Archive.zip\"</guimenuitem> creates these archive "
"types in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Stisni v \"Archive.tar.gz\"</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Stisni v \"Archive.zip\"</guimenuitem> ustvari te vrste arhivov "
"v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Compress to...</guimenuitem> opens a dialog where you can "
"select folder, name and archive type."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Stisni v ...</guimenuitem> odpre pogovorno okno, kjer lahko "
"izberete mapo, ime in vrsto arhiva."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Batch Mode"
msgstr "Napredni paketni način"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; has an advanced batch mode to manage archives without launching a "
"graphical user interface. This mode allows you to extract or create archives "
"and add files to them."
msgstr ""
"&ark; ima napreden paketni način za upravljanje arhivov brez zagona "
"grafičnega uporabniškega vmesnika. Ta način vam omogoča ekstrahiranje ali "
"ustvarjanje arhivov in dodajanje datotek vanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The batch mode is documented in <ulink url=\"man:/ark\">&ark;'s man page</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Paketni način je dokumentiran na <ulink url=\"man:/ark\">strani priročnika "
"&ark;</ulink>."

